'''木槿'''（{{lang-xm|Hibiscus syriacus}}）是[[锦葵科|锦葵科]][[木槿属|木槿属]]開花植物。原產於[[中国中南地区|中國中南]]、[[中国东南地区|東南地區]]，後引至[[亚洲|亚洲]]大部份地區在內的他處，廣爲種植。<ref name="POWO_560890-1">{{cite web |title=''Hibiscus syriacus'' L. |work=Plants of the World Online |publisher=Royal Botanic Gardens, Kew |url=http://www.plantsoftheworldonline.org/taxon/urn:lsid:ipni.org:names:560890-1 |access-date=2018-07-29 |archive-date=2020-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923012614/http://www.plantsoftheworldonline.org/taxon/urn:lsid:ipni.org:names:560890-1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>因收集自[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]花園，得[[种加词|种加词]]{{lang|la|''syriacus''}}。<ref>Lawton, B.P. 2004. Hibiscus – hardy and tropical plants for the garden. Timber Press, Portland, OR</ref><ref>Walker, J. 1999. Hibiscus. Cassel, London, England.</ref><ref>Alice M. Coats, ''Garden Shrubs and their Histories'' (1964) 1992, ''s.v.'' "Hibiscus".</ref>[[大韩民国|韓國]]又稱'''無窮花'''（{{kor|漢=無窮花|諺=무궁화|羅=mugunghwa}}），作为[[国花|国花]]出现於[[韩国国徽|国徽]]、[[愛國歌_(大韓民國)|國歌]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=National Administration> National Symbols of the Republic of Korea> The National Flower - Mugunghwa|url=https://www.mois.go.kr/eng/sub/a03/nationalSymbol_3/screen.do#:~:text=The%20National%20Flower%20-%20Mugunghwa,-Mugunghwa%20image&text=The%20mugunghwa,%20or%20the%20rose,of%20Korean%20culture%20for%20centuries.|access-date=2021-02-27|website=www.mois.go.kr|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225132516/https://www.mois.go.kr/eng/sub/a03/nationalSymbol_3/screen.do#:~:text=The%20National%20Flower%20-%20Mugunghwa,-Mugunghwa%20image&text=The%20mugunghwa,%20or%20the%20rose,of%20Korean%20culture%20for%20centuries.|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==特徵==
木槿是耐寒[[落葉植物|落葉]][[灌木|灌木]]。樹木直立，呈花瓶狀，高2－4公尺，有大喇叭形花，[[雄蕊|雄蕊]]呈白色而黃色尖端突出。<ref name=RHSAZ>{{cite book|title=RHS A-Z encyclopedia of garden plants|url=https://archive.org/details/azencyclopediaof0000unse|year=2008|publisher=Dorling Kindersley|location=United Kingdom|isbn=978-1405332965|pages=1136}}</ref>花通常呈粉色，也可呈近乎紫色的深粉、淺粉、白色。單朵花壽命短，僅開一天，但灌木能新生長出許多芽，從而在漫長的夏季花期內大量開花。木槿對空氣污染、高溫、潮溼、貧瘠、乾旱的耐受性很強。<ref>"Hibiscus Syriacus 'Notwoodtwo' WHITE CHIFFON – Plant Finder". Missouribotanicalgarden.org. N.p., 2016. Web. 21 Apr. 2017.</ref>木槿在許多郊區很好地歸化，甚至可能視爲輕度[[入侵物种|入侵物种]]。<ref name=NCState>{{Cite web|title=Hibiscus syriacus (Hibiscus, Rose of China, Rose of Sharon, Rose-of-Sharon, Shrub Althea) {{!}} North Carolina Extension Gardener Plant Toolbox|url=https://plants.ces.ncsu.edu/plants/hibiscus-syriacus/|access-date=2021-02-27|website=plants.ces.ncsu.edu|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125150017/https://plants.ces.ncsu.edu/plants/hibiscus-syriacus/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 
[[File:Hibiscus_syriacus_(12).JPG|thumbnail]]

===生長===
枝細而灰白，呈白色小齒狀，有凸起的葉疤痕和小芽。無修剪則莖和樹枝分支不會太多，許多長而直的莖從距地約1.5－4公分處長出，從而使灌木整體呈花瓶形狀。<ref name="Web 2017">plantfacts.osu.edu/pdf/0247-539.pdf. N.p., 2017. Web. 21 Apr. 2017.</ref>五月才長葉<ref name = TELE/>，通常呈綠色或淡黃綠色，互生，卵形或卵狀菱形，三淺裂，邊緣呈粗糙鋸齒狀<ref name="馬場篤">{{Cite book|author = 馬場篤|others = 大貫茂（写真）|script-title=ja: 薬草500種－栽培から効用まで|date = 1996-09-27|publisher = [[誠文堂新光社|誠文堂新光社]]|isbn = 4-416-49618-4|page =108|ref=harv}}</ref>。

===花===
[[File:Hibiscus_August_2010-2.jpg|alt=]]
木槿有五瓣花（直徑可至7.5公分）<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Hibiscus syriacus - Plant Finder|url=https://www.missouribotanicalgarden.org/PlantFinder/PlantFinderDetails.aspx?taxonid=282593&isprofile=1&basic=hibiscus%20syriacus|access-date=2021-02-27|website=www.missouribotanicalgarden.org|archive-date=2019-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190419142023/http://www.missouribotanicalgarden.org/PlantFinder/PlantFinderDetails.aspx?taxonid=282593&isprofile=1&basic=Hibiscus%20syriacus|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而呈白、紅、紫、淡紫、藍紫或藍色的純色，或有不同色喉的雙色花，因品種而異。從這五個花瓣基部伸出的是雌蕊，雄蕊環繞在雌蕊外圍。這些基本特徵使木槿及許多變種有與眾不同的形式。木槿通常七至九月每晚連續開花。<ref name=":0" />成熟後，柔軟的莖在大量夏季花朵的負載下變重，並彎曲到地面的一半。

===果實、種子===
大多數現代品種不結果。結果者果實呈綠或棕色，為五瓣裂開的[[蒴果|蒴果]]，某些較老的品種果實會宿存在樹上過冬。果實在休眠期結束後，會將易於發芽的種子散佈在親本植物的基部附近，隨時間形成群落。<ref name="Web 2017"/>

==種植==
儘管秋天也可以觀賞，修剪不當會生硬難看，但仍然是流行的觀賞灌木，有很多品種。成年植株可以耐多種不良條件，包括霜凍、乾旱、城市污染等。但溫暖、有遮蔽、[[土壤pH值|土壤呈中性]]而排水良好、陽光充足的環境結果最好。<ref name = TELE>{{cite web | last = Buchan | first = Ursula | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/gardening/howtogrow/3343918/Hibiscus-syriacus-how-to-grow.html | title = Hibiscus syriacus: how to grow | publisher = The Telegraph | access-date = 2018-11-28 | archive-date = 2018-11-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181128123025/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/gardening/howtogrow/3343918/Hibiscus-syriacus-how-to-grow.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>

===繁殖===
木槿很容易繁殖。使用種子繁殖時，後代會產生變異，植株和親本的性狀會有所不同。亦可以使用[[壓條|壓條]]、[[扦插|扦插]]等方式來[[无性生殖|複製]]原始植株<ref name="馬場篤" />。

===病蟲害===
木槿老灌木可能患最終致命的樹幹萎縮病。<ref>Cankers On Trees: Various. 1st ed. Cornell University College of Agriculture and Life Science, 2015. Web. 21 Apr. 2017.</ref>木槿對葉斑、枯萎病、鏽病和潰瘍病較敏感。有時會招[[日本金龜子|日本金龜子]]、[[粉虱科|粉蝨]]、[[蚜虫|蚜虫]]。若無控制，日本金龜子會嚴重破壞樹葉。

